"{\"uid\": \"metro.co.uk-2024-09-04-raygun-hits-back-criticism-olympic-breakdancing-routine-first-interview-21545934\", \"entities\": [{\"sentence\": \"Raygun is adamant that she was Australia's best female to represent her country at theOlympicsbut has apologised to the breakdancing community for her routines which went viral.\", \"from\": 0, \"to\": 177, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 0, \"end\": 6, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Raygun\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.0604298831774925e-20, \"text\": \"Raygun\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Raygun\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Raygun\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Rachael Gunn, who competes under the name 'Raygun',scored zero in all three of her heats as breakdancing made its Olympic debut in Paris this summer.\", \"from\": 179, \"to\": 328, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 179, \"end\": 186, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Rachael_Ray\", \"score\": 0.9999999978003871, \"rank\": 2.1908232746216504e-09, \"text\": \"Rachael\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Rachael_Ray\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Rachael_Ray\"}, {\"begin\": 187, \"end\": 191, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Clan_Gunn\", \"score\": 0.9305582555787136, \"rank\": 0.07272296860793546, \"text\": \"Gunn\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Clan_Gunn\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Clan_Gunn\"}, {\"begin\": 310, \"end\": 315, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 0.9999999798019419, \"rank\": 2.019816256327724e-08, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The 37-year-old created headlines around the world for her moves which included a kangaroo hop, a snake-like wriggle on the floor and the sprinkler.\", \"from\": 330, \"to\": 478, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Questions had been raised over Gunn's credentials but she claims that Australia needed 'more resources' in order to win an Olympic medal.\", \"from\": 480, \"to\": 617, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 511, \"end\": 515, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Clan_Gunn\", \"score\": 0.9305582555787136, \"rank\": 0.07272296860793546, \"text\": \"Gunn\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Clan_Gunn\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Clan_Gunn\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"On Wednesday, Gunn gave her first televised interview about her Olympic performance on Australia's Network 10 show 'The Project'.\", \"from\": 619, \"to\": 748, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 633, \"end\": 637, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Clan_Gunn\", \"score\": 0.9305582555787136, \"rank\": 0.07272296860793546, \"text\": \"Gunn\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Clan_Gunn\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Clan_Gunn\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Asked by The Project show host Waleed Aly whether she 'genuinely' feels she was the 'best female breaker in Australia', Gunn smiled and replied: 'I think my record speaks to that.'\", \"from\": 750, \"to\": 930, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 759, \"end\": 770, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/The_Project_(Australian_TV_program)\", \"score\": 0.9438574206613771, \"rank\": 0.05703744780054193, \"text\": \"The Project\", \"types\": [\"Q386724\", \"Q15416\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/The_Project_(Australian_TV_program)\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/The_Project_(Australian_TV_program)\"}, {\"begin\": 781, \"end\": 791, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Waleed_Aly\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Waleed Aly\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Waleed_Aly\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Waleed_Aly\"}, {\"begin\": 870, \"end\": 874, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Clan_Gunn\", \"score\": 0.9305582555787136, \"rank\": 0.07272296860793546, \"text\": \"Gunn\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Clan_Gunn\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Clan_Gunn\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"When asked about her qualification path to reach theOlympics, Gunn said: 'I was the top ranked Australian B-girl in 2020, and 2022, and 2023, I have been invited to represent at how many World Championships Paris, Korea, you know.\", \"from\": 932, \"to\": 1162, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 994, \"end\": 998, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Clan_Gunn\", \"score\": 0.9305582555787136, \"rank\": 0.07272296860793546, \"text\": \"Gunn\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Clan_Gunn\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Clan_Gunn\"}, {\"begin\": 1027, \"end\": 1037, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Australians\", \"score\": 0.999477246056199, \"rank\": 0.00041721445888074585, \"text\": \"Australian\", \"types\": [\"Q41710\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Australians\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Australians\"}, {\"begin\": 1139, \"end\": 1144, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 0.9999999798019419, \"rank\": 2.019816256327724e-08, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}, {\"begin\": 1146, \"end\": 1151, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/South_Korea\", \"score\": 0.9986564286908891, \"rank\": 0.0008407818257105915, \"text\": \"Korea\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/South_Korea\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/South_Korea\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"'So the record is there\\u2026 but anything can happen in a battle.\", \"from\": 1164, \"to\": 1225, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"You know, it's always about what happens on the day.\", \"from\": 1226, \"to\": 1278, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"That consistency shows, you know my level.'\", \"from\": 1279, \"to\": 1322, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"However, Gunn did admit that she knew her style would not be favoured by the judges in Paris.\", \"from\": 1324, \"to\": 1417, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1333, \"end\": 1337, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Clan_Gunn\", \"score\": 0.9305582555787136, \"rank\": 0.07272296860793546, \"text\": \"Gunn\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Clan_Gunn\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Clan_Gunn\"}, {\"begin\": 1411, \"end\": 1416, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 0.9999999798019419, \"rank\": 2.019816256327724e-08, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"'As soon as I qualified, I was like, 'oh my gosh, what have I done?'.\", \"from\": 1419, \"to\": 1488, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Because I knew that I was going to get beaten, and I knew that people were not going to understand my style and what I was going to do,' she said.\", \"from\": 1489, \"to\": 1635, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Gunn also said she is 'very sorry' after breakdancing was mocked following her appearance in Paris.\", \"from\": 1637, \"to\": 1736, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1637, \"end\": 1641, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Clan_Gunn\", \"score\": 0.9305582555787136, \"rank\": 0.07272296860793546, \"text\": \"Gunn\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Clan_Gunn\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Clan_Gunn\"}, {\"begin\": 1730, \"end\": 1735, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 0.9999999798019419, \"rank\": 2.019816256327724e-08, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"'It is really sad to hear those criticisms,' she said.\", \"from\": 1738, \"to\": 1792, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"'And I am very sorry for the backlash that the community has experienced, but I can not control how people react.\", \"from\": 1794, \"to\": 1907, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"'Unfortunately, we just need some more resources in Australia for us to have a chance to be world champions.\", \"from\": 1909, \"to\": 2017, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"'In the last year, I have trained my hardest.\", \"from\": 2019, \"to\": 2064, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"I have really put my body through it, put my mind through it.\", \"from\": 2065, \"to\": 2126, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"But if that's not good enough for someone, what can I say?'\", \"from\": 2127, \"to\": 2186, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"For more stories like this,check our sport page.\", \"from\": 2188, \"to\": 2236, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Follow Metro Sport for the latest news onFacebook,TwitterandInstagram.\", \"from\": 2238, \"to\": 2308, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"ArrowMORE:After climbing out of the bubble and being inspired by Paris 2024 diversity, the fire is lit for Olympic redemption  ArrowMORE:How blind Paralympians know which medal they have received  ArrowMORE:How many sports and medals are there at the Paris 2024 Paralympics?\", \"from\": 2310, \"to\": 2584, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2375, \"end\": 2385, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2024_Summer_Olympics\", \"score\": 0.9999999999979536, \"rank\": 1.9856518653119956e-12, \"text\": \"Paris 2024\", \"types\": [\"Q1656682\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2024_Summer_Olympics\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2024_Summer_Olympics\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Punchy analysis, transfer talk and more from Metro's football experts, sent straight to your inbox every week.\", \"from\": 2586, \"to\": 2696, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Let us know which team you sup